cello.alt.servlet.scripting
Class FileScript

java.lang.Object
  cello.alt.servlet.scripting.AbstractJavaScript
      cello.alt.servlet.scripting.FileScript
All Implemented Interfaces:
JavaScript
public class FileScript
extends AbstractJavaScript

A simple File-based implementation of JavaScript. It uses the file modification time to decide whether it has been updated or not. Efficiency note: Every time the script is used (directly or indirectly), this will make a call to File.lastModified().

Author:
Marcello
